      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "It depends on what you actually want to achieve. Maybe you are actually looking for <code>java -Djava.library.path=...</code>? However, to get <code>DYLD_*</code> variables working with <code>&#47;usr&#47;bin&#47;java</code>, you would need to completely <a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/documentation/security/disabling_and_enabling_system_integrity_protection\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">disable SIP</a>."
    } ],
    "owner" : {
